resources.string: Lottie is a library for Android, iOS, Web, and Windows that parses Adobe After Effects animations exported as json with Bodymovin and renders them natively on mobile and on the web! For the first time, designers can create and ship beautiful animations without an engineer painstakingly recreating it by hand.
